Comment: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:26.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.18,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Hey, weed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.47,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,This is our third meeting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.23,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,And you still haven't learned your lesson. {underestimate the hell out of me}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:45.31,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I'll kill you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.98,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Come on, bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:51.48,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.70,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Didn't you guys tell me not to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:08.84,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he just touch{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.48,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Ready for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.11,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's only targeting Jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:48.79,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was he confusing us with his declaration earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:50.33,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}And not just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.55,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}He has also deactivated his Limitless technique!
Comment: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.93,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:06.31,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}Using his technique in this crowded space\N would require extreme precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:10.02,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he planning to stick to close combat\N with just cursed energy manipulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.78,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that case, I don't need to blend in with the crowd anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:23.91,Default,Hanami,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't need to hold back on using my technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.34,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Don't deactivate Domain Extension, Hanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.05,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I heard this is your weak spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.14,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:50.35,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Domain Extension and innate techniques\N can't be used at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.94,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only reason I'm still alive is because \NI was protecting myself with Domain Extension.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.49,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's this strong with just physical attacks and\N basic cursed energy manipulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:06.24,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gojo Satoru, is there anything you're {\i0}not{\i1} capable of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.16,Default,Choso,0,0,0,,Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.42,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not a cursed spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:15.04,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be one of the Death Painting Womb incarnations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.75,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Annoying, but he'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:21.55,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:29.68,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,The more you try to neutralize my technique\N with Domain Extension, the more I will reinforce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:34.11,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,You think this asparagus here\N has the energy left to handle that?
Comment: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.23,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.71,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Gojo Satoru! I'll kill them all! {Look over here}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.23,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Hanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.53,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:27.62,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,The Prison Realm is a living barrier{\fscx180}—{\fscx}the remains of Genshin. {genshin. the monk. implied to be his innate domain. which also implies that cursed objects are just made out of sorcerers, or at least their techniques.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:30.58,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,There is nothing that Prison Realm can't seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:36.54,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,In that case, there must be some conditions to using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.17,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.43,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:48.14,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Once the Prison Realm's gate is opened,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:51.89,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,the target must be in its four-meter\N sealing range for one whole minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.89,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That's where you need to keep Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.80,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Hold up. {no reason not to meme}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:31.26,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,I will burn you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:37.44,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Surely you didn't join forces just to\N push that impossible task onto us, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:42.57,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,To keep that thing under\N those conditions for one whole minute
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:46.86,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,even a thousand measly \Nhuman lives wouldn't be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.37,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Things are getting a little heated here, Jogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.49,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.45,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,When I say one minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.86,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let Hanami's death be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:32.12,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blend into the crowd. Focus on hit-and-runs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.17,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Choso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:45.17,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,If you don't help, I'll kill you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.30,Default,Choso,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.89,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not too close, not too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.98,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not gonna work for long, though. {og:But that's the best they can do.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:02.40,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}People who can't see curses\N are starting to move away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:07.36,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}As their numbers keep dwindling,\N once there's enough space, I can catch Volcano Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:11.28,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I doubt I could trick them\N by deactivating my technique again. {og:No more releasing my technique to lure it in like before.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.95,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've revealed my goal of \Nbeating them to a pulp in close combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:19.96,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll be a problem if they unleash a\N large-scale coordinated attack on the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:25.29,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. I won't be able to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.88,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in return...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:32.64,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will make sure they're exorcised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.26,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:37.22,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\i1}It must have been twenty minutes by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.23,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.98,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Gojo Satoru is still completely composed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.90,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,We need him more on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:06.21,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Hey, are you oka{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:10.92,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Everyone... into monsters... on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.76,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,I... I was told...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:17.93,Cursed,Woman,0,0,0,,The train was full! Didn't need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.85,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,He was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:24.69,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.61,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.15,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}...on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.15,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}There are eight carriages on the incoming train. {almost missed the italics here}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.53,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please stand behind the yellow line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.53,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,{*}Mr. Gojo{*Gojo-sensei}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:40.49,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please do not put your hands or head\N beyond the platform door, or lean against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.84,Default,People,0,0,0,,Train's here! Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.05,Default,People,0,0,0,,We can go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.19,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:09.65,Default,People,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:10.52,Default,People,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.32,Default,People,0,0,0,,Let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:11.86,Default,People,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:12.65,Default,People,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.61,Default,People,0,0,0,,It's the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.82,Default,People,0,0,0,,Outta my way! I'm gettin' in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.49,Default,Man,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:18.37,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Can we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.16,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.65,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,What the hell are they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:54.61,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Jogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.74,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Man, the air smells so nice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:03.45,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Full of fear and dread!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.12,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,We should totally keep a few humans alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.92,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,We'll release them into the forest\N and hunt them on the weekends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.42,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Can I burn down the forest along with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:13.42,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Hanami would get upset over that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:15.97,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,Hanami is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.97,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Comment: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:24.01,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.16,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Whoa! I can't hit you for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.54,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Patchface!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.37,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one Nanami and Yuji mentioned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.93,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Do you know what I find so disgusting about humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.10,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,There's just too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.90,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,There must be more of them above. {the phrase "cursed spirits or curse users" is used too many times in this arc when it clearly doesn't need to be spelled out. gege pls.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.24,Default,Choso,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(480,1020)}Blood Manipulation:\NConvergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.24,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(1440,1020)}Idle Transfiguration:\NSoul Multiplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.24,Default,Choso,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(960,480)}Supernova.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:22.24,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Body Repel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:47.93,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike Itadori Yuji, Gojo Satoru is\N capable of making cold decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:54.31,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know he's willing to make sacrifices\N if it means exorcising us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.11,0:13:59.28,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}But with the rising number of\N humans killed and about to be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:03.36,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}how many sacrifices can he justify?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.70,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}You have but one option right now:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:14.96,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}Use your Infinite Void to kill us along with \Nevery human here to save the ones outside the domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.46,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}But you are incapable of doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:22.59,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}The only sacrifices you're willing to accept\N are people killed by curses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:26.68,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}not people killed by Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.73,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}Now, think and agonize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.89,Default,Jogo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)\i1}Until you're on the edge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.07,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)}No way! {Ain't}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.24,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)}Domain Expansion:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.49,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1020)}Infinite Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:20.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was an all or nothing Domain Expansion of only 0.2 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:29.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The duration was decided by Gojo Satoru purely on instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:35.75,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was the amount of time he believed non-sorcerers could withstand Infinite Void
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.67,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,without suffering lasting effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:52.14,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,During those 0.2 seconds,\N roughly half a year's worth of information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:56.39,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,flowed into the brains of non-sorcerers\N and transfigured humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.65,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,rendering every one of them unconscious on their feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:22.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,In the aftermath, all the survivors from B5\N were able to return to society two months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.71,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,That's how precise his Infinite Void was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:41.27,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,That also meant the special-grade cursed spirits\N could reawaken at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:47.28,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,With the possibility of a counterattack in mind, \NGojo Satoru narrowed his targets to the transfigured humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:13.10,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Upon deactivation of the domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:19.85,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,roughly 1,000 transfigured humans\N unleashed upon B5 were annihilated in 299 seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:24.15,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,at the hands of the strongest sorcerer\N of the modern age. {oh shit i should've kept that "strongest sorcerer of the modern age" line in 28} {great, now they got "the strongest sorcerer in history vs the strongest sorcerer of today"} {after a long discussion, the tldr is this: different translations in different contexts is fine}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.68,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Prison Realm: Gate, Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.23,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.03,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,When I say one minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:25.79,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,'Sup,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:29.67,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.67,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.18,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.43,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:44.52,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some transformation technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.32,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it really is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:05.25,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It's one minute's worth of time in Gojo Satoru's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:17.34,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Come now, Satoru. You shouldn't\N lose yourself in thought in the midst of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.85,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't sense any cursed energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.93,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't even move a muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.77,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this game over? {it's gojover}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.69,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,So, who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.23,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I'm Geto Suguru, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:34.11,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Don't you remember me? How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:40.95,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Whether it's your body or your cursed energy,\N my Six Eyes tell me you're Geto Suguru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.29,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.50,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,My {\i1}soul{\i0} denies it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.21,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Now, give me a straight answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.97,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:00.80,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.40,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.32,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That is my technique, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:20.16,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I can hop between bodies\N by replacing its brain with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.41,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,It also lets me use the body's \Ninnate techniques, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:27.83,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I needed his Curse Manipulation and this exact situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:33.25,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Back then, you didn't have Ieiri Shoko\N handle the disposal of Geto Suguru's body, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:40.05,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,That was an odd time for you to show consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:43.05,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I was able to obtain this body with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:47.27,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You needn't worry. The seal will be broken eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:52.02,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,In a hundred... no, maybe a thousand years from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:54.02,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,You're just too strong. {GEGE WHEN I CATCH YOU}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.99,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,And you're in the way of my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.74,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:04.49,Default,Gojo,0,0,0,,Before it was killed by me, who was it that\N beat the crap out of that body?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.75,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Okkotsu Yuta, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:10.83,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,I really don't get what everyone sees in that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:17.92,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,His ability to copy techniques unconditionally\N as well as his boundless cursed energy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:24.51,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,are both merely a result of the Binding Vow that\N links him with the soul of his beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:30.77,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Sorry to say this, but Okkotsu Yuta \Nwill never be you. {this is not foreshadowing... is it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.24,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Gojo Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:42.78,Default,Geto,0,0,0,,We'll meet again in the new world. {wait............. could this be what gojo said to geto? or sth similar at least, like the line from the OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.37,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,What the{\fscx180}—{\fscx}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.46,Default,Ui,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.21,Default,Yuji,0,0,0,,There's... something on my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:56.21,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Itadori Yuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.92,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\pos(999,1020)}There's no time.\N Listen carefully, I'll only say this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:08.22,Default,Mechamaru,0,0,0,,{\pos(999,1020)}Gojo Satoru has been sealed.
